<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="dracula">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow">
    <title>Setup Complete - Admin Panel</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/dracula.css">
    <style>
        body {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            background: var(--background);
            color: var(--foreground);
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
        }

        .setup-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .setup-card {
            background: var(--current-line);
            border: 1px solid var(--comment);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 3rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .setup-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .setup-title {
            margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--green);
        }

        .setup-description {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: var(--foreground);
            font-size: 1.125rem;
        }

        .info-box {
            background: var(--background);
            border: 1px solid var(--comment);
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .info-box h3 {
            margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--purple);
        }

        .info-box ul {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
        }

        .info-box li {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: var(--foreground);
        }

        .admin-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0.5rem;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            background: var(--purple);
            color: var(--background);
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }

        .admin-link:hover {
            background: #9580ff;
        }

        .admin-link-secondary {
            background: var(--selection);
            color: var(--foreground);
        }

        .admin-link-secondary:hover {
            background: var(--comment);
        }

        .setup-button {
            margin-top: 1rem;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            background: var(--green);
            color: var(--background);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }

        .setup-button:hover {
            background: #5af78e;
        }

        .isolation-note {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            padding: 1rem;
            background: rgba(139, 233, 253, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid var(--cyan);
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: var(--cyan);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="setup-container">
        <div class="setup-card">
            <div class="setup-icon">âœ…</div>
            <h1 class="setup-title">Setup Complete!</h1>
            <div class="setup-description">
                <p>Congratulations! Your admin account has been created and the server is configured.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <h3>Admin Panel Access</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Your admin credentials have been set</strong></li>
                    <li>You can now manage server settings and configuration</li>
                    <li>Configure SSL/TLS, email, and notifications</li>
                    <li>Manage API tokens and security settings</li>
                    <li>Set up scheduled tasks and backups</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <h3>Next Steps</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Review server settings and branding</li>
                    <li>Configure SSL/TLS certificates (recommended)</li>
                    <li>Set up email notifications (SMTP)</li>
                    <li>Enable scheduled backups</li>
                    <li>Review security settings</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Admin Panel Links Only (per AI.md PART 18 - No public route links) -->
            <div style="margin: 2rem 0;">
                <a href="/admin/dashboard" class="admin-link">Go to Dashboard</a>
                <a href="/admin/server/settings" class="admin-link admin-link-secondary">Server Settings</a>
            </div>

            <!-- Note about admin panel isolation per AI.md PART 18 -->
            <div class="isolation-note">
                <strong>Admin Panel Isolation:</strong> This admin panel is completely separate from the public site.
                To access the public weather interface, open a new browser tab and navigate to the server's homepage.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
